WEBVTT

00:13:57.720 --> 00:14:00.936
is to have courageous conversations

00:14:00.960 --> 00:14:03.176
with difficult people,

00:14:03.200 --> 00:14:06.616
people who do not see the world
the same way that you see the world?

00:14:06.640 --> 00:14:11.496
Oh yes, folks, conversations may be
indeed the key to that upgrade,

00:14:11.520 --> 00:14:13.056
because remember,

00:14:13.080 --> 00:14:16.096
language was the first form
of virtual reality.

00:14:16.120 --> 00:14:20.216
It is literally a symbolic representation
of the physical world,

00:14:20.240 --> 00:14:23.296
and through this device,
we change the physical world.

00:14:23.320 --> 00:14:26.456
Keep in mind, conversations stop violence,

00:14:26.480 --> 00:14:28.616
conversations start countries,

00:14:28.640 --> 00:14:29.896
they build bridges,

00:14:29.920 --> 00:14:31.456
and when the chips are down,